{"tid":767262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺32隊世界杯，只係得亞根廷足協同教練有問題。","createTime":"2018-08-04T10:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T05:16:19.000Z","uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17ccdb50b1b90f6de0ee4923e308b4171af568d3","tid":767262,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母阿根廷，你地肯醒未？<br />\n攞咁多次亞軍都未識痛定思痛。<br />\n一次又一次柒出國際，<br />\n全世界得你請個教練同球員唔夾。<br />\n排陣又排到舊屎咁。<br />\n又搞小圈子，鍾意出邊個就出邊個。<br />\n鍾意就出美沙，有伊卡迪又唔撚用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好笑既係，一次又一次亞軍，阿根廷都睇唔到個問題係邊。每一次都係足協，貪污，教練，重用廢球員。<br />\n醒啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"713debfb0569cbca8b990acce028ee0115cd27aa","tid":767262,"uid":67225,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"認為鳩蛇煩到仆街嘅請正皮"},{"pid":"47fb0fddbc8fbd08980c0c4123cbe03a32d4cbe3","tid":767262,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"713debfb0569cbca8b990acce028ee0115cd27aa","tid":767262,"uid":67225,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"認為鳩蛇煩到仆街嘅請正皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"煩乜鳩野，駁我都要搵point。<br />\n講中晒就話人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c341b65011c7bf1dfc3498f9953bd413e0a627","tid":767262,"uid":67225,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"47fb0fddbc8fbd08980c0c4123cbe03a32d4cbe3","tid":767262,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"713debfb0569cbca8b990acce028ee0115cd27aa","tid":767262,"uid":67225,"like":33,"dislike":5,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"認為鳩蛇煩到仆街嘅請正皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"煩乜鳩野，駁我都要搵point。<br />\n講中晒就話人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"無興趣駁你<br />\n只係覺得你煩到仆街"},{"pid":"cdab55474256db7f3fefbe429fa604a2e86723b4","tid":767262,"uid":158145,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedB